org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT spree_stock_locations.* FROM spree_stock_locations INNER JOIN spree_stock_items ON spree_stock_items.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_stock_items.stock_location_id = spree_stock_locations.id WHERE spree_stock_locations.active = "$1" AND spree_stock_items.variant_id IN ("$2", "$3")

rewrites.sql: SELECT spree_stock_locations.* FROM spree_stock_locations WHERE spree_stock_locations.active = "$1"
